o evidence shows U.S. forces remained to hold, govern, or administer any Venezuelan territory after the two-hour operation\n\n**Conclusion:**\nUnder the preponderance standard, the admitted record does not prove the specific intent to establish territorial control. The stronger evidence shows the operational object was capture and extraction, with temporary tactical control serving that purpose rather than a plan to possess or administer Venezuelan land.\n\nTherefore, I find the proposition **not demonstrated**.","contentIndex":0,"partial":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"arguments":{"args":"{\"vote\":\"not_demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The record proves a serious U.S. military raid inside Caracas but official sources and credible reporting consistently frame the operational objective as capture/extraction, not territorial control; the decisive intent element remains unproved under a preponderance standard.\"}","tool":"aar_submit_council_vote"},"id":"EDfTweru0","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"mistralai/mistral-medium-3-5","provider":"openrouter","responseId":"gen-1782779612-A65mphVo3MKIaxeTsYOw","responseModel":"mistralai/mistral-medium-3.5-20260430","role":"assistant","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782779612663,"usage":{"cacheRead":40224,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"input":0,"output":0,"total":0},"input":3431,"output":545,"totalTokens":44200}},"type":"text_end"},"message":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"arguments":{"args":"{\"vote\":\"not_demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The record proves a serious U.S. military raid inside Caracas but official sources and credible reporting consistently frame the operational objective as capture/extraction, not territorial control; the decisive intent element remains unproved under a preponderance standard.\"}","tool":"aar_submit_council_vote"},"id":"EDfTweru0","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"mistralai/mistral-mediu