juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Official U.S. source admitting oil-revenue custody, blockade, lethal-force authorization, and an armed forces operation against Maduro within the case window.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T00:20:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"0c5c88687b2a889093788193bdd900106b95ff6ccfab1af50709f67df61cb673\",\"size_bytes\":1819,\"source_description\":\"White House fact sheet page, extracted via web.open on 2026-06-30.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/fact-sheets/2026/01/fact-sheet-president-donald-j-trump-safeguards-venezuelan-oil-revenue-for-the-good-of-the-american-and-venezuelan-people/\",\"storage_name\":\"0c/0c5c88687b2a889093788193bdd900106b95ff6ccfab1af50709f67df61cb673\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"PX-1 White House fact sheet on Venezuelan oil revenue and U.S. operation\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T00:24:59Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_26011b5f6d79_submitted-evidence-06-defendant-26011b5f6d79\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-06-defendant-26011b5f6d79.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Official source on Operation Absolute Resolve showing both adverse facts (Caracas operation and transition comments) and defense facts (capture/extraction, criminal proceedings, joint military/law-enforcement mission, no U.S. casualties, anti-narcoterrorism context).\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T00:29:30Z\",\"sha256\":\"26011b5f6d792bc39d1eabe168123482dcc270e34745035055127683c27c55e1\",\"size_bytes\":2203,\"source_description\":\"Department of War/Pentagon News article by Matthew Olay, opened via web.open on 2026-06-30.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.war.gov/News/News-Stories/Article/Article/4370431/trump-announces-us-militarys-capture-of-maduro/\",\"storage_name\":\"26/26011b5f6d792bc39d1eabe168123482dcc270e34745035055127683c27c55e1\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"